2571883,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxMzgyNTcxODgz","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/labels/package:%20components","name":"package: components","color":"d4bbff","default":false,"description":"carbon-components"},{"id":1692677297,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxNjkyNjc3Mjk3","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/labels/component:%20data-table","name":"component: data-table","color":"a6c8ff","default":false,"description":""},{"id":1692683661,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxNjkyNjgzNjYx","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/labels/component:%20tooltip","name":"component: tooltip","color":"a6c8ff","default":false,"description":""},{"id":3010846448,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwzMDEwODQ2NDQ4","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/labels/package:%20styles","name":"package: styles","color":"d4bbff","default":false,"description":"@carbon/styles"}],"state":"open","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2021-11-28T11:11:35Z","updated_at":"2022-01-06T18:36:48Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"### Package\r\n\r\ncarbon-components\r\n\r\n### Browser\r\n\r\nChrome\r\n\r\n### Package version\r\n\r\nv10.48.0 (via carbon-components-svelte)\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nThe `Tooltip` component has an inverted color scheme, so `Link` colors within it also get inverted. However, this style can be overridden when the `Tooltip` is within a `DataTable` and the row is directly or indirectly hovered.\r\n\r\n[Link color inversion in Tooltip](https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon/blob/c017826bc77864fbe8af7b8ac0c9039d29c9c630/packages/components/src/components/tooltip/_tooltip.scss#L453):\r\n```scss\r\n  .#{$prefix}--tooltip {\r\n    // ...\r\n    .#{$prefix}--link {\r\n      color: $inverse-link;\r\n      font-size: rem(14px);\r\n```\r\n\r\n[DataTable override on hover](https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon/blob/c017826bc77864fbe8af7b8ac0c9039d29c9c630/packages/components/src/components/data-table/_data-table-core.scss#L96):\r\n```scss\r\n  .#{$prefix}--data-table tbody tr:hover td .#{$prefix}--link,\r\n  .#{$prefix}--data-table tbody tr:hover th .#{$prefix}--link {\r\n    color: $link-secondary;\r\n  }\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Screenshots\r\n\r\nWithout hover:\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/834235/143765131-f17b4393-5186-4d67-8a68-e3f1af600db6.png)\r\n\r\nWith hover:\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/834235/143765140-8c6e3f59-b579-464c-acf7-a1b4ff2e5cad.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n- Add `DataTable`\r\n- Add `Tooltip` with `Link` to one of the cells\r\n- Open tooltip and hover row or tooltip popup\r\n\r\n[Svelte REPL](https://svelte.dev/repl/db0d79b1e9494ec9a108be63b842005e?version=3.44.2)\r\n\r\n### Code of Conduct\r\n\r\n- [X] I agree to follow this project's [Code of Conduct](https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon/blob/f555616971a03fd454c0f4daea184adf41fff05b/.github/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md)\r\n- [X] I checked the [current issues](https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues) for duplicate problems","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10182/reactions","total_count":1,"+1":1,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10182/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"score":1},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/9874","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/9874/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/9874/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/9874/events","html_url":"https://github.com/carbon-de